323
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:55,420
Liang that means forgiveness.

324
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:56,720
Liang that means consideration.

325
00:15:56,980 --> 00:15:58,180
Liang that means understanding.

326
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:02,100
They affectionately call me

327
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:03,140
Su.

328
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:05,340
I understand

329
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:07,340
every word you Tang people speak,

330
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:09,300
but you

331
00:16:09,580 --> 00:16:10,500
might not

332
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:12,740
