336
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:20,540
Don't

337
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:22,900
worry unnecessarily.

338
00:16:23,780 --> 00:16:24,700
Well...

339
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:26,060
Well, the way you use idioms...

340
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:34,700
Well, what do you want?

341
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:39,620
Envoy Li.

342
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:41,220
You like to get straight to the point?

343
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:43,340
I like it too.

344
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:48,060
You must have run into

345
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:49,660
big trouble

346
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:52,660
