347
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:55,020
Am I right?

348
00:16:59,740 --> 00:17:00,660
Well...

349
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,340
So

350
00:17:04,340 --> 00:17:05,300
I guessed it right?

351
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,300
Don't worry, Envoy Li.

352
00:17:09,820 --> 00:17:11,540
I have money.

353
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:13,220
I

354
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,460
can lend it to you.

355
00:17:15,060 --> 00:17:16,620
You can lend me money?

356
00:17:18,060 --> 00:17:18,980
Of course.

357
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:20,060
We merchants

358
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:21,260
prefer

359
00:17:21,980 --> 00:17:22,900
exchange.

360
00:17:24,260 --> 00:17:25,740
Shrimp for fish.

361
00:17:26,340 --> 00:17:27,860
Fish for shrimp.

