00:17:28,940 --> 00:17:31,700
Sea turtle for pangolin.

363
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,700
I don't have a pangolin.

364
00:17:34,780 --> 00:17:36,460
I don't need a sea turtle either.

365
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,380
I want

366
00:17:39,620 --> 00:17:41,580
to exchange something

367
00:17:41,980 --> 00:17:42,900
with you.

368
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:44,620
I don't have

369
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:46,180
anything valuable.

370
00:17:47,100 --> 00:17:48,020
Just now,

371
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:50,060
that fat,

372
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:52,180
handsome friend said

373
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:56,100
you travel freely in Lingnan

374
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:57,820
without any inspection

375
00:17:58,180 --> 00:17:59,300
