376
00:18:00,300 --> 00:18:01,220
I guess

377
00:18:01,580 --> 00:18:02,500
you must have obtained

378
00:18:02,660 --> 00:18:04,300
a travel pass.

379
00:18:12,580 --> 00:18:14,740
I do have

380
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:17,955
a Five Prefectures Pass.

