00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:19,980
So I

382
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,140
guessed it right.

383
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:24,300
The goods aren't limited.

384
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,500
The pass is empty

385
00:18:26,900 --> 00:18:27,700
