386
00:18:27,700 --> 00:18:28,540
Right?

387
00:18:28,540 --> 00:18:29,860
It's indeed blank.

388
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:33,700
Great.

389
00:18:35,020 --> 00:18:38,666
Can you lend it to me first?

390
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:41,200
It will help me with my business.

391
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:43,133
How much money do you need?

392
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:43,940
Name a price.

393
00:18:43,940 --> 00:18:45,300
I'll pay you now.

394
00:18:45,740 --> 00:18:46,660
This way,

395
00:18:46,900 --> 00:18:48,780
you'll get a sea turtle,

396
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:50,980
and I'll have a pangolin.

397
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:53,580
While we fight like clam and snip,

398
00:18:53,580 --> 00:18:54,888
the fisherman benefits.

399
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:56,990
No, you didn't use this idiom
