403
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:04,460
I like that very much.

404
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:08,688
A promise made after three drinks

405
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:11,222
matters more than the five mountains.

406
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:12,860
Li Bai said that.

407
00:19:13,540 --> 00:19:14,820
Why are you reciting poetry?

408
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:15,300
Well...

409
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,260
If we Tang people

410
00:19:16,740 --> 00:19:19,660
impersonate others,

411
00:19:20,140 --> 00:19:21,260
we'll be killed.

412
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:22,740
I understand.

413
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:24,260
Of course, I understand.

414
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:25,460
So

415
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:27,180
I won't let you suffer a loss.

416
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:29,820
I'll give you a big advantage.

417
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:31,820
Name a price.

418
00:19:32,340 --> 00:19:33,820
I'll pay you right away.

419
00:19:40,300 --> 00:19:41,260
766.

420
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:42,500
It's a deal.

421
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:44,180
It's a deal?

422
00:19:44,460 --> 00:19:46,620
If you think it's too little, I can add

423
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:47,820
another 30%.

424
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:50,980
Let's make it a whole number.

425
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,140
1,000 guan.

426
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,220
What do you think?

427
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:54,860
No.

428
00:19:54,860 --> 00:19:56,220
766 plus 30% of it

429
00:19:56,220 --> 00:19:57,140
is 996.

430
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:59,340
996 then.

431
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,100
It's a deal.

432
00:20:04,260 --> 00:20:05,180
Be careful.

433
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:10,780
Watch your step.

434
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:18,020
Slow down.

435
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:21,460
Walk slowly.

436
00:20:24,580 --> 00:20:26,380
(20 Guan)

437
00:20:26,380 --> 00:20:28,740
(33 Guan)

438
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:29,980
Shande, you're amazing.

439
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:34,244
He gave you extra,
yet you insisted on reducing the amount.

440
00:20:36,380 --> 00:20:37,820
I just blurted it out.

441
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:38,980
I couldn't take it back.

442
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:41,660
I've never seen anyone

443
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:45,022
who treats a budget
like a final account like you.

444
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:48,700
But we underestimated

445
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:49,340
this pass's

446
00:20:49,340 --> 00:20:50,700
potential value to merchants.

447
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:52,140
I bet he'll accept

448
00:20:52,140 --> 00:20:53,100
even if you ask

449
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:54,380
for 1,500 guan.

450
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:57,860
Seeing how readily he agreed,

451
00:20:58,300 --> 00:21:00,022
I'm a bit regretful too.

452
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:04,180
Anyway,

453
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,780
you gained a lot.

454
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,820
Are you leaving today?

455
00:21:10,060 --> 00:21:11,420
Before coming here,

456
00:21:11,450 --> 00:21:13,900
I went to Ministry of War's
Geography and Local Records Bureau

457
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,340
and copied a copy
of Map of Imperial Tang's Nine Provinces

458
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:18,100
and Comprehensive Records
of Post Stations.

459
00:21:18,140 --> 00:21:19,500
I now have a clear understanding

460
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:20,900
of Tang Dynasty's transportation.

461
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:23,020
(Last night,)

462
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:25,020
(I spent the whole night
planning in the room.)

463
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:27,580
(After leaving Chang'an,)

464
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:29,860
enter Shangzhou's path from Lantian.

465
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:32,180
Cross Han River through Xiangzhou.

466
00:21:32,780 --> 00:21:33,940
(Then, head south,)

467
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:36,820
(cross the river through Ezhou.)

