00:21:37,140 --> 00:21:39,420
Follow the river
to Hongzhou, Jizhou, Qianzhou.

469
00:21:39,660 --> 00:21:41,700
Cross the Wuling through Mei Pass
to Shaozhou.

470
00:21:41,900 --> 00:21:42,860
To reach Lingnan,

471
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:43,860
the total is

472
00:21:43,860 --> 00:21:45,580
2723.5 km.

473
00:21:46,860 --> 00:21:49,300
If 0.5 km consumes one guan,

474
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:50,180
that's

475
00:21:50,180 --> 00:21:51,620
5,447 guan.

476
00:21:53,660 --> 00:21:54,620
But I have no money

477
00:21:54,620 --> 00:21:56,460
after coming to Lingnan.

478
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:58,220
I never tried it.

479
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:00,020
Try what?

480
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,333
Transport litchis?

481
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:04,020
If I manage to transport litchis,

482
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:05,660
I won't have to die.

483
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:07,540
Xiu'er will have her father.

484
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:08,860
You'd better die.

485
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:11,660
How can you
have the idea of â€‹â€‹transporting litchis?

486
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:13,900
Now that you have money,
hurry back to Chang'an.

487
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:16,266
Save yourself from unnecessary delays
and complications.

488
00:22:17,300 --> 00:22:19,060
Before leaving, Zimei said

489
00:22:20,180 --> 00:22:22,020
I took a fatal mission,

490
00:22:22,260 --> 00:22:23,940
but I might find a way to live

491
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:25,340
in a desperate situation.

492
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:27,660
I was swayed.

493
00:22:27,940 --> 00:22:29,260
Shande, don't be swayed.

494
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:31,980
Zimei is a poet.

495
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,200
He doesn't bother with details.

496
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:34,700
He just said some stuff in Chang'an,

497
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:35,620
and you're swayed.

498
00:22:36,140 --> 00:22:37,660
Find a way to live?

499
00:22:38,300 --> 00:22:40,380
You're likely to fall into the abyss.

500
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:42,900
If Inspector's Office finds out
you sold the travel pass,

501
00:22:43,940 --> 00:22:44,940
you're still doomed.

502
00:22:45,260 --> 00:22:46,500
But I haven't even seen

503
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:47,620
a litch tree.

504
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:48,820
I can't accept it.

505
00:22:48,820 --> 00:22:49,980
Why do you see that?

506
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:51,930
Just go back to Chang'an and see Xiu'er!

507
00:22:52,460 --> 00:22:54,100
She's alone in Chang'an.

508
00:22:56,020 --> 00:22:56,980
If my sister were alive,

509
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:59,140
she wouldn't
let you do whatever you want.

510
00:23:05,940 --> 00:23:06,860
Gou'er.

511
00:23:08,260 --> 00:23:09,180
Here.

