535
00:24:43,355 --> 00:24:45,380
The Lantern Festival
of the 3rd year of Tianbao?

536
00:24:45,660 --> 00:24:46,580
Could it be...

537
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,140
Yes.

538
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:52,780
The water is cold.

