541
00:24:57,540 --> 00:24:58,460
Jijiang.

542
00:25:01,580 --> 00:25:02,340
Uncle.

543
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:04,000
Get another basin of clean water.

544
00:25:04,380 --> 00:25:05,300
Yes.

