00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:12,620
Left Chancellor.

546
00:25:13,660 --> 00:25:15,020
After Wuji's house was confiscated,

547
00:25:15,620 --> 00:25:16,940
the dismissed servants

548
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:18,100
have

