00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:43,300
because there was hope.

590
00:26:47,060 --> 00:26:47,980
Over the years,

591
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:49,700
I've been secretly

592
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:52,390
investigating the evidence
of Right Chancellor's corruption.

593
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:53,540
Wuji

594
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,380
vowed to bring down Right Chancellor.

595
00:26:55,980 --> 00:26:57,220
He was not even afraid

596
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:58,420
of death.

597
00:27:00,820 --> 00:27:01,740
Who knew

598
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:04,420
his words would come true?

599
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:06,380
Now,

600
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:08,420
Right Chancellor framed Wuji again.

601
00:27:08,940 --> 00:27:09,860
He said

602
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:12,260
he used me

603
00:27:12,460 --> 00:27:14,300
to extort local officials.

604
00:27:14,820 --> 00:27:16,820
He also executed Wuji

605
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:18,340
without authorization.

606
00:27:19,460 --> 00:27:20,380
How dare he say

607
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:22,140
it's to preserve my reputation?

608
00:27:25,780 --> 00:27:26,700
I know

609
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:28,500
he's lying,

610
00:27:30,140 --> 00:27:32,460
but I can't do anything.

611
00:27:34,700 --> 00:27:35,740
We can only

612
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:37,740
endure

613
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:40,820
to avoid losing the big picture
for small matters.

614
00:27:42,220 --> 00:27:43,140
You

615
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:44,900
should avoid suspicion all the more

616
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:47,820
to prevent Right Chancellor's followers
from making a fuss

617
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:49,060
about Wuji again

618
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:51,700
and causing a rift

619
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:54,088
between His Majesty and Left Chancellor.

620
00:27:58,140 --> 00:27:59,100
He Youguang

621
00:27:59,100 --> 00:28:01,100
asked me for the military tally

622
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:03,866
to mobilize the navy

623
00:28:03,911 --> 00:28:06,500
to recruit the surrounding pirates.

624
00:28:07,060 --> 00:28:09,020
Over the years, he colluded

625
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:10,220
with Lingnan's officials.

626
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:11,180
He's quite capable

627
00:28:11,180 --> 00:28:13,020
and has a huge influence there.

628
00:28:15,020 --> 00:28:18,140
He wants to make it
his personal playground.

629
00:28:18,140 --> 00:28:19,060
Afterward,

630
00:28:19,780 --> 00:28:20,700
his money

631
00:28:21,020 --> 00:28:24,780
is laundered through Hu merchants
before being brought into Chang'an.

632
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:26,020
That way,

633
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:29,180
it'll be watertight.

634
00:28:31,420 --> 00:28:32,620
Since he's

635
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:34,140
loyal to me

636
00:28:34,140 --> 00:28:35,220
all these years,

637
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:38,180
let's help him.

638
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:41,020
(Send someone reliable)

639
00:28:41,140 --> 00:28:42,060
(to Lingnan)

640
00:28:42,460 --> 00:28:43,580
(and deliver this message)

641
00:28:43,980 --> 00:28:45,180
(to Ma Guiyun.)

642
00:28:45,860 --> 00:28:47,020
(Tell him to stay there)

643
00:28:47,220 --> 00:28:49,920
(and wait until the matter is resolved
before returning to Chang'an.)

644
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,500
The information

645
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:57,860
that Song Wuji found in Lingnan
must have been seized

646
00:28:57,860 --> 00:28:58,860
by Right Chancellor.

647
00:28:58,860 --> 00:28:59,740
(Security Bureau)

648
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:01,930
(Right Chancellor sent his men
out of the city overnight.)

649
00:29:01,933 --> 00:29:03,177
They're heading toward Gaozhou.

650
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:05,280
This way,

651
00:29:05,280 --> 00:29:07,800
Lingnan is even more dangerous.

652
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:11,444
