You don't need to worry too much.

654
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,520
This person is quite clever.

655
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:18,920
He must be able to deal with it.

656
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:20,320
More importantly,

657
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:23,460
he wants to be accepted back
into the Zheng family.

658
00:29:24,733 --> 00:29:27,755
