are the easiest to control.

659
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,520
(If his identity is exposed,)

660
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,920
(he's just an Assistant Minister
of Entertainment.)

661
00:29:34,155 --> 00:29:35,555
(We can just give him up.)

662
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:38,560
(Konglang won't let him leave Lingnan.)

663
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,080
Mr. Li, take care.

664
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,040
Gou'er.

665
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:09,520
Go and report to Inspector's Office

666
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:10,800
that Litchi Envoy is gone.

667
00:30:11,210 --> 00:30:13,380
Have them arrange someone
to verify at the city gate.

668
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,840
Yes.

669
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:20,360
Mr. Li.

670
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:21,640
Guiyun.

671
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:23,360
It's a long way to Chang'an.

672
00:30:24,840 --> 00:30:26,720
I don't know when we'll meet again.

673
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,120
Take care.

674
00:30:38,460 --> 00:30:40,320
Green hills stretch across
the northern wall.

675
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,000
White water
flows around the eastern city.

676
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:46,920
We bid farewell here.

677
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:50,520
You'll travel far away.

678
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,700
The drifting clouds
reflect the traveler's feelings.

679
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:58,040
The sunset mirrors a friend's affection.

680
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,320
Wave goodbye.

681
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:03,840
The horses neigh mournfully.

682
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:08,360
I'm not very talented

683
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:10,240
and can't come up with a good poem.

684
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:13,280
I can only borrow
a few lines from Li Bai

685
00:31:14,200 --> 00:31:15,120
to express my feelings.

686
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:16,920
Mr. Li.

687
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,280
The journey is dangerous.

688
00:31:19,760 --> 00:31:20,680
Take care.

689
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:35,480
Since you gave me a poem,

690
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,320
