691
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,360
No need to be so polite.

692
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:39,800
No, we can't break the rules.

693
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:41,600
It's getting late.

694
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,520
I got one.

