I got one.

696
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:50,240
I'm headed north
toward my hometown that's far away.

697
00:31:51,688 --> 00:31:55,200
My sleeves are wet with tears.

698
00:31:55,933 --> 00:31:58,760
I bid farewell from horseback
without paper or brush.

699
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:03,800
I'll write back
to assure you all is well.

700
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,480
This is a poem by Cen Shen.

701
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,760
I edited it.

702
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:08,880
The original poem is...

703
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,880
I understand.

704
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,160
Yours is better than Cen Shen's.

705
00:32:11,160 --> 00:32:12,520
You mentioned yourself and safety.

706
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:13,960
Mr. Li.

707
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:16,400
Don't worry that no one knows you.

708
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:18,120
Everyone knows you.

709
00:32:19,822 --> 00:32:20,822
Time to go.

710
00:32:24,080 --> 00:32:25,000
- Yes!
- Yes!

711
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:32,240
(Litchi Bureau)

712
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,080
Where are you going?

713
00:32:45,560 --> 00:32:48,080
We're escorting a convoy to Chang'an.

714
00:32:48,580 --> 00:32:50,240
This carriage driver
