720
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:01,800
What's in this?

721
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,080
Who is this?

722
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,960
His name is Chen A-di.

723
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:15,000
Chen A-di.

724
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:36,320
