Ten coins.

744
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:29,230
This is her litch orchard.

745
00:34:34,830 --> 00:34:35,830
Sir.

746
00:34:35,830 --> 00:34:37,510
This is where the Dong people

747
00:34:37,510 --> 00:34:38,870
plant the litch trees.

748
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:40,030
But

749
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:41,070
it has just bloomed,

750
00:34:41,155 --> 00:34:42,430
and the fruit hasn't matured.

751
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:44,710
Take a look.

752
00:34:45,670 --> 00:34:47,190
This doesn't look pleasant.

753
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:49,390
Even Zimei

754
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:50,790
can't write much about this.

755
00:34:51,150 --> 00:34:52,150
Sir.

756
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,190
The litch trees

757
00:34:53,190 --> 00:34:54,310
might not look great.

758
00:34:54,870 --> 00:34:57,310
These are litchis
grown by Gaozhou's Dong people.

759
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,630
They're the best.

760
00:34:59,430 --> 00:35:01,230
Especially the Dong girl
you're looking for.

761
00:35:01,510 --> 00:35:02,430
Her name is Tong.

762
00:35:02,750 --> 00:35:03,830
The litchis she grows

763
