hers.

770
00:35:16,630 --> 00:35:17,550
Sir.

771
00:35:18,133 --> 00:35:19,022
Payment.

772
00:35:19,622 --> 00:35:21,355
I can't come here for nothing, can I?

773
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:22,430
Here.

774
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:23,470
Find ten coins.

775
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:24,790
Sure, don't worry.

776
00:35:26,790 --> 00:35:27,710
Look.

777
00:35:29,830 --> 00:35:31,310
Let's forget about the rest.

778
00:35:31,470 --> 00:35:32,070
Forget it?

779
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:32,790
Well...

780
00:35:32,790 --> 00:35:33,830
Forget it.

781
00:35:58,470 --> 00:35:59,430
You...

782
00:35:59,430 --> 00:36:00,430
A city folk

783
00:36:00,430 --> 00:36:01,590
wearing official robes!

784
00:36:02,190 --> 00:36:04,550
- Where?
- Where?

785
00:36:06,850 --> 00:36:08,840
There's indeed a city folk
wearing official robes.

786
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:11,910
