came to confiscate our orchard.

787
00:36:11,910 --> 00:36:13,190
We chased that one away.

788
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:15,610
This one is probably newly assigned
by Inspector's Office.

789
00:36:17,830 --> 00:36:19,110
Litchi Bureau.

