Inspector He is quite attentive.

793
00:36:27,977 --> 00:36:29,511
I'm Litchi Envoy.

794
00:36:30,911 --> 00:36:32,377
You're willing to die for litchis, huh?

795
00:36:32,444 --> 00:36:33,950
It's willing to die for money!

796
00:36:33,950 --> 00:36:34,870
Attack!

797
00:36:39,790 --> 00:36:40,510
Ban.

