815
00:37:13,133 --> 00:37:14,190
It rained a few days ago.

816
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:15,310
Could it be stink bugs?

817
00:37:15,630 --> 00:37:16,550
No.

818
00:37:21,430 --> 00:37:22,950
It's Lady Stoneback.

819
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:24,670
Isn't this a stink bug?

820
00:37:25,270 --> 00:37:26,190
No.

821
00:37:26,430 --> 00:37:28,110
We set up bamboo ropes between the trees

822
00:37:28,110 --> 00:37:29,250
