823
00:37:29,350 --> 00:37:30,470
They'll kill Lady Stoneback.

824
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:31,750
Your method

825
00:37:31,750 --> 00:37:32,670
won't work.

826
00:37:32,790 --> 00:37:34,550
Stink bugs can fly.

827
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:36,310
Ants can't catch them.

828
00:37:36,310 --> 00:37:37,110
Untie me.

829
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:38,130
