are filled with stinky juice.

832
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,710
It smells awful and won't come off.

833
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,830
It won't come off with water.

834
00:37:49,870 --> 00:37:50,830
There's mint.

835
00:37:51,030 --> 00:37:52,230
Wipe it with mint leaves.

836
