Smell it.

843
00:38:13,950 --> 00:38:15,240
It really doesn't stink anymore.

844
00:38:15,390 --> 00:38:16,350
It works, right?

845
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:18,590
Let me tell you.

846
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,110
Stink bugs

847
