Here, let's peel together.

857
00:38:37,870 --> 00:38:38,790
Hurry.

858
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,590
Does anyone
have a black locust for washing clothes?

859
00:38:54,690 --> 00:38:55,830
I have black locusts at home.

860
00:38:55,990 --> 00:38:57,070
Go get it.

861
00:38:57,350 --> 00:38:57,910
Get some water

862
00:38:57,910 --> 00:38:59,630
and make black locust juice.

863
00:38:59,630 --> 00:39:00,590
Half of you

864
00:39:00,990 --> 00:39:02,470
can pick the mint leaves.

865
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:04,230
Squeeze them into juice too.

866
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,430
Water is here.

867
00:39:06,690 --> 00:39:07,310
Here, make way.

868
00:39:07,310 --> 00:39:08,390
The black locust is here.

869
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:09,070
Here.

